name: Vizam
Lore: 'Kajain''sa''Nikto. Keeps Jabba''s vehicles and starships well armed. Has hidden several weapon caches on board Jabba''s sail barge.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 when defending a battle. If with your Advosze during your control phase, may search Reserve Deck, take one vehicle weapon into hand and reshuffle. Your vehicle weapons deploy free at same site.',
